@model UpdateUserViewModel
<h4 class="fw-bold py-3 mb-4"><span class="text-muted fw-light">Hesap Ayarları /</span>Kullanıcı Detayı</h4>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <form id="formAccountSettings" method="POST">
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <h5 class="card-header">Profil Detayı</h5>
                <!-- Account -->
                <hr class="my-0" />
                <div class="card-body">

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="mb-3 col-md-6">
                            <label for="name" class="form-label">Ad</label>
                            <input class="form-control" type="text" id="name" name="name" value="@Model.Name" autofocus />
                            <span asp-validation-for="Name" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3 col-md-6">
                            <label for="surname" class="form-label">Soyad</label>
                            <input class="form-control" type="text" name="surname" id="surname" value="@Model.Surname" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="Name" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3 col-md-6">
                            <label asp-for="Email" class="form-label">E-mail</label>
                            <input class="form-control" type="text" sp-for="Email"
                                   placeholder="mail@example.com" readonly />
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3 col-md-6">
                            <label class="form-label" asp-for="Phone">Cep Telefonu</label>
                            <div class="input-group input-group-merge">
                                <span class="input-group-text"></span>
                                <input type="text" asp-for="Phone" class="form-control"
                                       placeholder="555 555 0111" readonly />
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3 col-md-6">
                            <label asp-for="OperationClaimId" class="form-label">Yetki</label>
                            <select class="form-select" asp-for="OperationClaimId" aria-label="OperationClaimId">
                                @foreach (var role in Model.Roles)
                                {
                                    <option value="@role.Id">@role.Name</option>
                                }
                            </select>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-2">
                        <input type="hidden" asp-for="Id" />
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Güncelle</button>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <!-- /Account -->
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h5 class="card-header">Hesabı Sil</h5>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="mb-3 col-12 mb-0">
                        <div class="alert alert-warning">
                            <h6 class="alert-heading fw-bold mb-1">Hesabı silmek istediğinizden emin misiniz?"</h6>
                            <p class="mb-0">Hesabı silmenin kalıcı olduğunu ve hesap sahibinin erişim sağlayamayacağını unutmayın.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-check mb-3">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" asp-for="IsDeleted" />
                        <label class="form-check-label" asp-for="IsDeleted">
                            Hesabın devre dışı bırakılmasını
                            onaylıyorum
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger deactivate-account">Hesabı Sil</button>

                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>